l.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65279f72a1a23445a18028bc01d7981547835dc6","tid":1850323,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:13:34.000Z","msg":"讓病毒穿透坦克"},{"pid":"c3abbd65e9e983417b4e861db9ccd33abbba2f99","tid":1850323,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:34:11.000Z","msg":"德豬：排華不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7059d394be4bb424ea0b30f720795dcde8ffab2","tid":1850323,"uid":38255,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:11:52.000Z","msg":"呢單要睇埋個細節可以好大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一階段：患者去過湖北<br />\n第二階段：患者無去過湖北但接觸過去過湖北既人<br />\n第三階段：患者無去過無接觸過去過湖北既人但有接觸過確診病人<br />\n第四階段：患者無去過湖北無接觸過任何確診或者去過湖北既人<br />\n<br />\n除左睇人數，仲要睇感染方式，香港雖然有10單但暫時全部都去過湖北仲係階段一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日本有8單已經有1個係階段二<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />德國呢單如果後面果3個有接觸過個上海妹就仲係階段二<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果無同過個上海妹交流只係同患者一號接觸都奶野，就會係唯一一個外國已經同中国一樣去到階段三<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大鑊好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes20.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes50.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes500.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而中国放出黎既消息仲未去到階段四實情唔知<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102571d8616532caa0be5b61096a74825f88e068","tid":1850323,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:15:36.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎 已感染德國。"},{"pid":"337577074cbf272376e28d52c5fca0a4882cac84","tid":1850323,"uid":282404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f7059d394be4bb424ea0b30f720795dcde8ffab2","tid":1850323,"uid":38255,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:11:52.000Z","msg":"呢單要睇埋個細節可以好大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一階段：患者去過湖北<br />\n第二階段：患者無去過湖北但接觸過去過湖北既人<br />\n第三階段：患者無去過無接觸過去過湖北既人但有接觸過確診病人<br />\n第四階段：患者無去過湖北無接觸過任何確診或者去過湖北既人<br />\n<br />\n除左睇人數，仲要睇感染方式，香港雖然有10單但暫時全部都去過湖北仲係階段一<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日本有8單已經有1個係階段二<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />德國呢單如果後面果3個有接觸過個上海妹就仲係階段二<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果無同過個上海妹交流只係同患者一號接觸都奶野，就會係唯一一個外國已經同中国一樣去到階段三<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大鑊好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes20.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes50.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes500.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而中国放出黎既消息仲未去到階段四實情唔知<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />謝謝分析"},{"pid":"29bfb35086674b87b02d12f555b0d0e23173e857","tid":1850323,"uid":136150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"垃圾徳國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces